    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hi guys,</p>\r\n<p>I am introducing now Prism to our new project in the company. :) <br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe project is WPF4.</p>\r\n<p>A normal Button on my View can perfectly connect to the ViewModel however if I have the button inside a Style/Template, I get an error:</p>\r\n<pre style=\"font-family:Consolas; background:white; color:black; font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Style</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;x</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:red\">Key</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;DatagridColumnHeaderCustomTemplateStyle&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;TargetType</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">x</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Type</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;DataGridColumnHeader</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;<br><pre style=\"font-family:Consolas; background:white; color:black; font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:blue\">   &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Setter</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Property</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;Template&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Setter.Value</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">ControlTemplate</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;TargetType</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">x</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Type</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;DataGridColumnHeader</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Grid</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;MouseLeftButtonDown</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;Grid_MouseLeftButtonDown&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;<br><pre style=\"font-family:Consolas; background:white; color:black; font-size:13px\"><span style=\"color:blue\">                          &lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Button</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Width</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;50&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Content</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;RelativeSource</span><span style=\"color:blue\">={</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">RelativeSource</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;FindAncestor</span><span style=\"color:blue\">,</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;AncestorType</span><span style=\"color:blue\">={</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">x</span><span style=\"color:blue\">:</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Type</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;DataGrid</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}},</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">DataContext</span><span style=\"color:blue\">.</span><span style=\"color:blue\">MultiSortCommand</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Command</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=&quot;{</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">Binding</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;MultiSortCommand</span><span style=\"color:blue\">}</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:red\">&nbsp;Grid.Row</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&quot;1&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&nbsp;/&gt;</span>\r\n</pre>\r\n<br></span></pre>\r\n</span></pre>\r\n<p><br>\r\nError<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>'CommandConverter' is unable to convert 'Microsoft.Practices.Prism.Commands.DelegateCommand' to 'System.String'.</strong></p>\r\n<p>Any idea? Its a tough nut :(<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanks,<br>\r\nHouman</p>\r\n",
